class.name: MetaPlatformSDK_ChallengeEntryArray
class.description: An array of [MetaPlatformSDK_ChallengeEntry]s. [b]NOTE:[/b] This isn't a Godot [Array], but you can loop over it using [code]for x in arr[/code] just like a Godot [Array].

method.name: get_element
method.description: Returns an element in the array by index.

method.name: has_next_page
method.description: Returns [code]true[/code] if there is next page of elements.

method.name: has_previous_page
method.description: Returns [code]true[/code] if there is previous page of elements.

method.name: size
method.description: Returns the size of the array.

members.member: The URL used to request the next page of elements.
The URL used to request the previous page of elements.
The total count of elements on all pages.
